Ticket - package Ticket
 
Ticket - Class in Ticket
Consists of basic information on the person getting a ticket, their vehicle, and the reason for the ticket.
Ticket() - Constructor for class Ticket.Ticket
 
TicketController - Class in Ticket
Connects the model and the view by handling events from the view and sending them to the model.
TicketController(TicketModel, TicketView) - Constructor for class Ticket.TicketController
 
TicketGUI - Class in main
Calls on TicketModel, TicketView, and TicketController to create a GUI ticket citation system
TicketGUI() - Constructor for class main.TicketGUI
 
TicketModel - Class in Ticket
Provides a model to store tickets
TicketModel() - Constructor for class Ticket.TicketModel
 
TicketView - Class in Ticket
Provides a GUI for inputing ticket information and displaying payment information
TicketView() - Constructor for class Ticket.TicketView
 
TicketView() - Method in class Ticket.TicketView
TicketView Constructor Sets up the GUI that is divided in five parts: a form with TextFields in the center, a title banner on top, a text area with payment information on the right, a navigation panel on the left for cycling through tickets, and a display area on the bottom for viewing tickets.
